data.description: Beautiful 1 story Single Family Home located in a gated community to enjoy privacy and security in a serene neighborhood. Discover this stunning home with high ceilings, where natural light radiates a vibrant atmosphere. Generous lot size for outdoor activities, future expansions, relaxation, gardening or outdoor entertainment. This residence offers an ample space and provides cozy personal spaces for everyone. 3 Bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and double garage. TVs, washer and dryer are not included in sale of the property.  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!
